{"tid":1069294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「這不是支那製造」 1罐瓶裝水讓支蝗玻璃心碎","createTime":"2019-03-20T01:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T08:54:12.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1185,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b1c7dcfc867e59d642bd7b4f4bdc5d35ddcd46","tid":1069294,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"中國玻璃心又碎一地！有網友今日在《微博》分享照片，指稱在南非連鎖超市見到一款瓶裝水，瓶身上竟強調「這罐水並非中國製造」（It's not made in China），該圖一出，立刻引發許多中國網友不滿，甚至有中國網友在微信上呼籲抵制這項產品。<br />\n <br />\n名為「外星人的空白格」的網友今日下午在在《微博》分享一張瓶裝水的照片，並指在南非有家連鎖超市出現該款瓶裝水，瓶身上則寫著，這罐水並非由中國製造，瓶子的側面還寫上「愛護地球，買本地產品」、「做一個主動微笑的人，別做那種沒禮貌的冷臉子」。就連廠商的註冊網站也是以此命名，網址「<a href=\"http://www.itsnotmadeinchina.co.za\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itsnotmadeinchina.co.za&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9CZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=0fc93b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.itsnotmadeinchina.co.za</a>」，讓PO文者懷疑根本是刻意要昭告天下，他們與中國絕無任何關係，該圖PO出後也引發許多中國網友不滿，甚至在微信群組上呼籲抵制這款產品，以及留言給該廠商進行抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpNStOYl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpNStOYl.jpg&h=0d4ff760&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6136e389ebf070d0fe7257d28a77bad9c7f776aa","tid":1069294,"uid":164043,"like":887,"dislike":1,"score":886,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"幫我入十箱"},{"pid":"ca9a1974e5ec4bc8e2406c2a5aa43f6a37608d03","tid":1069294,"uid":21545,"like":677,"dislike":7,"score":670,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"證明你支那個朵幾臭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89170d4a4938da7a099323fe39cc37c764e02b8f","tid":1069294,"uid":238189,"like":1041,"dislike":4,"score":1037,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"又冇係你國家發售，抵制乜鳩"},{"pid":"bed6765136f36879a1855af24acd22258e6e7276","tid":1069294,"uid":34777,"like":449,"dislike":3,"score":446,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:06